Package fr.umlv.wallj.game

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Cell
    Represents a cell in the grid of a board.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    A board represents a whole level of a game.
    CollisionHandler
    Manages the collision in the JBox2D world.
    Empty
    Empty is a cell where the elements can move.
    Game
    The main class of the game.
    Garbage
    Garbage is the element that the player must destroy to win.
    Player
    Represents a player in the game.
    Sizes
    Contains constants used by the game, in order to change them easily if needed.
    Trashcan
    Trashcan allows to the player to destroy the garbages.
    Wall
    Wall represents a basic obstacle, the garbages bounce on it.
